import { useEffect, useContext, useState, useRef } from "react"; import TopNav from "../../topNav/js/topNav"; import "../css/longs.css"; import { UseContextValues } from "../../../App"; export default function LongsComp() { const videoInfo = useContext(UseContextValues); const [uryFirstVideo, setUryFirstVideo] = useState({}); const [urySecondVideo, setUrySecondVideo] = useState({}); const [urySubs, setUrySubs] = useState({}); const [beterVideo, setBeterVideo] = useState({}); const [beterSubs, setBeterSubs] = useState({}); const middleElement = useRef(null); useEffect(() => { console.log(videoInfo); setUryFirstVideo(videoInfo.uryFirstVideo); setUrySecondVideo(videoInfo.urySecondVideo); setUrySubs(videoInfo.urySubs); setBeterVideo(videoInfo.beterVideo); setBeterSubs(videoInfo.beterSubs); }, [videoInfo.fetchingResult]); function activeSelectedVideo(e) { middleElement.current.children.forEach(ele => { ele.children[1].style.cssText = ""; }); e.currentTarget.children[1].style.cssText = "border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color)"; } return (
activeSelectedVideo(e)} className="video-holder-main-container">
{urySecondVideo.views}
{urySecondVideo.likes}
{urySubs.subscribers} subscribers
activeSelectedVideo(e)} className="video-holder-main-container">
{uryFirstVideo.views}
{uryFirstVideo.likes}
{urySubs.subscribers} subscribers
activeSelectedVideo(e)} className="video-holder-main-container">
{beterVideo.views}
{beterVideo.likes}
{beterSubs.subscribers} subscribers
); }
